==English==

===Pronunciation===
\rih-FULL-junss\

===Noun=== 
: a radiant or resplendent quality or state; brilliance 

====Example====
Cervantes' [[Don Quixote]] compares his beloved's hair to "threads of the brightest gold of Araby, whose refulgence dimmed the sun himself."

